                        <div class="container">
                            <div class="row">
                                <div class="col-auto col-sm-12 col-md-11 col-lg-8 col-xl-7">
                                    <h1 class="inn-banner-header-text">About Us</h1>
                                    <p class="banner-text-sml">The Synergy Low Code Digital Transformation Platform is built as a modular tool to fit into your business environment seamlessly.<br><br>Get to know the company behind the code more closely!</p>
