                                        <div class="row">
                                            <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-6 col-xl-6">
                                                <p>Low-code digital transformation by Synergy is simply adaptable and may be used by all corporate sectors, including banking, healthcare, government, oil and gas, construction and infrastructure, manufacturing, real estate, hospitality (hotels and restaurants), and so on.<br></p>
                                                <div class="row">
                                                    <div class="col-xl-6">
                                                        <ul class="synergyList">
                                                            <li class="p-2">Government/Public Sector</li>
                                                            <li class="p-2">Financial Institutions/Banks</li>
                                                            <li class="p-2">Construction/Infrastructure</li>
                                                        </ul>
                                                    </div>
                                                    <div class="col-xl-6">
                                                        <ul class="synergyList">
                                                            <li class="p-2">Telecom/Call Centers</li>
                                                            <li class="p-2">Retail/Hospitality</li>
