                                            <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-12 pt-10">
                                                <p>Synergy low-code digital transformation is intended to assist businesses in digitalizing their day-to-day processes and reducing manual labour in an easy and cost-effective manner.<br></p>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-12">
                                <h2 class="text-muted main-title-bg">Our Culture<br></h2>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col">
                                <div class="card flex-grow-1 flex-shrink-1 flex-fill">
                                    <div class="card-body text-left text-sm-left text-md-left text-lg-left text-xl-left">
                                        <div class="row">
                                            <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-12 pt-10">
                                                <ul class="synergyList">
                                                    <li class="p-2">We are a customer-centric firm that values both external and internal customers.<br></li>
                                                    <li class="p-2">We believe in empowering our staff and pushing them to think creatively and to take strategic risks.<br></li>
                                                    <li class="p-2">We believe in an open-door approach that allows leaders and employees to openly communicate, as well as leaders that walk the walk and provide effective direction to all employees.<br></li>
                                                    <li class="p-2">In the face of change, we are very adaptive and flexible, and we encourage our people to be imaginative. We place a high value on any suggestions made by our staff.<br></li>
                                                </ul>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-12">
                                <h2 class="text-muted main-title-bg">Benefits we provide to your business</h2>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col">
                                <div class="card flex-grow-1 flex-shrink-1 flex-fill">
                                    <div class="card-body text-left text-sm-left text-md-left text-lg-left text-xl-left">
                                        <div class="row">
                                            <div class="col-12 col-sm-12 col-md-12 col-lg-12 col-xl-12">
                                                <ul class="synergyList">
                                                    <li class="p-2">Rapid digitization and greater work collaboration to enable remote working.<br></li>
                                                    <li class="p-2">Increasing process efficiency and effectiveness through multitasking, automatic follow-ups, and KPI evaluation.<br></li>
                                                    <li class="p-2">It collects data from all base systems in one location so that swift judgments may be made.<br></li>
                                                    <li class="p-2">It provides centralized layers that are coupled with basic systems to enable for flexible and simple-to-implement operations.<br></li>
                                                    <li class="p-2">It provides tools for assigning and tracking employee tasks, which improves accountability.<br></li>
                                                </ul>
                                            </div>
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
